9. f3 Bf5 {This is a lesser evil compared to 9....Bh5. However, White achieves an 
advantage here as well.} 10. Bxf5 exf5 11. Bf4 $1 {Using the e-file discovery, White 
deploys his bishop to an optimal position.} Nge7 12. Qg3 $14 {White preserves an edge 
thanks to his comfortable piece placement and better structure.} *

