{A radical, yet hardly satisfactory solution to the problem of the light-squared 
bishop. The bishop pair and control of the center give White excellent long-term 
prospects.} 9. Qxe2 Bd6 10. g3 Nf6 11. Nd2 O-O 12. f4 $14 {White is ready to occupy 
the e5 square with his knight and prepare a kingside assault.} *

