9. Ng3 $1 Nf6 {This modest move is objectivelly better than 9....h5, but it makes the 
whole 8....Be7 move order appear counterproductive.} 10. f3 Bh5 11. Nxh5 Nxh5 12. f4 
$14 {The position is analogous to the one resulting from the 8....Bxe2 line.} *

